ntandquests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=700.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   New Spawns on the Bee isle in PoA</span><hr size=1> This weekend we were clearing the bee island in PoA.  The left spawn, that splits like the pegusus isle, and the middle spawn, that spawns the boss, are still the same.  However, the right spawn, that used to spawn 3 level 55 Bazzazzats now spawn these new bees called Bizzts or Bzzzts... The name is really really short.  Not only is their name short, their lifespawn is too.  They have very low hit points, too short to even bother casting on so the resists don't matter.  They aren't easy though, you'll lose people fighting them fast cause they hit fast and they hit for 1200's. You can take them down quick with melee, but there are 3 of them, and they'll tear through everyone whil you're killing them.  Just a warning.  Also, if anyone else has fought them, please post any info you have on them. We weren't able to get a level or a resist rate on them.  Same drops as the other bees... <p>~~
<BR>
<BR>Sarion Ifrinteine
<BR>Arch Mage
<BR>Master of the Elements
<BR>Heroic Few
<BR>Morell-Thule</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uabmagfab.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AbMagFab</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 406<br> <font color=#333333>(6/4/01 3:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerequipmentandquests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=700.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: New Spawns on the Bee isle in PoA</span><hr size=1> <br>
